    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Habitus, dorsal view. A Heterarthrodes alvimi IBSP 50, syntype 3; B Stenoprostygnus mamillatus IBSP 10100, holotype 3; C Leitaoius iguapensis IBSP 10552, syntype 3; D Mitogoniella mutila IBSP 10551, holotype Ƥ; E Adelphobunus singularis IBSP 17, holotype 3; F – G Anomaloleptes singularis IBSP 4 (F syntype 3, G syntype Ƥ); H Chaquesia minensis IBSP 10088, syntype Ƥ; I Diplocaldasius pallidus IBSP 10, holotype Ƥ. Scale lines: 1 mm: B; 5 mm: A, C – I." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219892/files/figure.png" ;
